3 If ye then be risen with Christ, seek those things which are above, where Christ sitteth on the right hand of God.

And we know that the Son of God is come, and hath given us an understanding, that we may know him that is true, and we are in him that is true, even in his Son Jesus Christ. This is the true God, and eternal life.





3 Surely he shall deliver thee from the snare of the fowler, and from the noisome pestilence.

4 He shall cover thee with his feathers, and under his wings shalt thou trust: his truth shall be thy shield and buckler.

Colossians 1:13-14 King James Version (KJV)

13 Who hath delivered us from the power of darkness, and hath translated us into the kingdom of his dear Son:

14 In whom we have redemption through his blood, even the forgiveness of sins:

Galatians 3:13 King James Version (KJV)

13 Christ hath redeemed us from the curse of the law, being made a curse for us: for it is written, Cursed is every one that hangeth on a tree:



5 Thou shalt not be afraid for the terror by night; nor for the arrow that flieth by day;

9 For in him dwelleth all the fulness of the Godhead bodily.

10 And ye are complete in him, which is the head of all principality and power:

2 Thessalonians 3:3

But the Lord is faithful, who shall stablish you, and keep you from evil

11 For he shall give his angels charge over thee, to keep thee in all thy ways.

12 They shall bear thee up in their hands, lest thou dash thy foot against a stone.

Hebrews 1:14

Are they not all ministering spirits, sent forth to minister for them who shall be heirs of salvation?

The Most High is our Dwelling Place, we are Complete In Him, The Lord will Deliver us From All Evil. The Angels are Charge over Us, they Minister to us who are Heirs of Salvation. They Bear us up in their Hands. He Stablishes us.

13 Thou shalt tread upon the lion and adder: the young lion and the dragon shalt thou trample under feet.

Luke 10:19

Behold, I give unto you power to tread on serpents and scorpions, and over all the power of the enemy: and nothing shall by any means hurt you.



In Christ, we have Authority to Tread on Serpents, an Scorpions and all the Power of the devil, In Jesus Name, we Cast out Devils.

14 Because he hath set his love upon me, therefore will I deliver him: I will set him on high, because he hath known my name.

4 But God, who is rich in mercy, for his great love wherewith he loved us,

5 Even when we were dead in sins, hath quickened us together with Christ, (by grace ye are saved;)

15 He shall call upon me, and I will answer him: I will be with him in trouble; I will deliver him, and honour

Romans 10:13

For whosoever shall call upon the name of the Lord shall be saved him.



Hebrews 9:12

Neither by the blood of goats and calves, but by his own blood he entered in once into the holy place, having obtained eternal redemption for us.

We called upon the Name of the Lord Jesus and were saved. We have Redempion, Deliverance by His Blood, We were made Alive, Quickened with Zoe, Raised and Seated with Jesus in the Heavenlies In Christ!



16 With long life will I satisfy him, and shew him my salvation

10 For with the heart man believeth unto righteousness; and with the mouth confession is made unto salvation.

Ephesians 2:7 That in the ages to come he might shew the exceeding riches of his grace in his kindness toward us through Christ Jesus.





We have Salvation In Christ, we were shown His Salvation and were Saved. We are being Shown the riches of our Inheritance In Christ Jesus!
